Bristol-Myers Squibb, Princeton, NJ.[7] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[8] "Product Information. Trikafta (elexacaftor/ivacaftor/tezacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[9] "Product Information. Kalydeco (ivacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[10] "Product Information. Orkambi (ivacaftor-lumacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.[11] "Product Information. Symdeko 4-Week (ivacaftor-tezacaftor)." Vertex Pharmaceuticals, Cambridge, MA.', 1767369485);
