nteractions between ethanol and trazodone or amitriptyline." Neuropsychobiology 15 (1986): 31-7[8] "Product Information. Rexulti (brexpiprazole)." Otsuka American Pharmaceuticals Inc, Rockville, MD.', 1767369485);
